OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FKeir Starmer has said he condemns "in
OL,8,Fthe strongest terms" Iranian attacks
OL,9,Fon shipping and oil and gas facilities
OL,10,Fin the Gulf, in a joint statement with
OL,11,Fallied world leaders.
OL,13,FIn a written statement, the leaders of
OL,14,FFrance, Germany, Italy, the
OL,15,FNetherlands and Japan condemned Iran's
OL,16,Flatest wave of attacks and urged the
OL,17,Fcountry to "cease its threats" and
OL,18,Fcomply with international law.
OL,26,@oD@cOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe statement comes after Iran
OL,8,Fattacked Qatari liquefied natural gas
OL,9,Ffacilities and two Kuwaiti oil
OL,10,Frefineries overnight - the latest
OL,11,Fescalation of the ongoing conflict.
OL,13,FIran's strikes came after an Israeli
OL,14,Fattack on its main natural gas fields.
OL,16,FThe attack has seen gas prices spike
OL,17,Frapidly overnight - with UK natural
OL,18,Fgas prices reaching a three year high
OL,19,Fon Thursday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FIn their statement, the leaders also
OL,8,Fcondemned Iran's "de facto closure of
OL,9,Fthe Strait of Hormuz by Iranian
OL,10,Fforces".
OL,12,FThe prime minister said the UK was
OL,13,Fready to "contribute to appropriate
OL,14,Fefforts" to re-open the major oil
OL,15,Froute - and was working with allies to
OL,16,Fstabilise energy prices and boost
OL,17,Finternational oil supplies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"We welcome the International Energy
OL,8,FAgency decision to authorise a
OL,9,Fcoordinated release of strategic
OL,10,Fpetroleum reserves. We will take other
OL,11,Fsteps to stabilise energy markets,
OL,12,Fincluding working with certain
OL,13,Fproducing nations to increase output,"
OL,14,Fthe statement read.
OL,16,FThe intervention comes as the Defence
OL,17,FSecretary John Healey said the UK
OL,18,Fwould "step up the defensive support"
OL,19,Fthe UK is offering to Gulf states
OL,20,Ffollowing the latest strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"They're a serious escalation," he
OL,8,Fsaid. "They further destabilise the
OL,9,Fregion and we will step up the
OL,10,Fdefensive support that we can offer to
OL,11,Fthose Gulf states."
OL,13,FSpeaking on a visit to Dreghorn
OL,14,FBarracks in Edinburgh, Healey also
OL,15,Fconfirmed UK military planners joined
OL,16,Fthe US Central Command to help
OL,17,Fformulate proposals for opening the
OL,18,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
