PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FIranian missiles hit the Ras Laffan
OL,8,Fliquefied natural gas plant in Qatar
OL,9,Fovernight on Wednesday - causing what
OL,10,Fthe Qatari authorities have called
OL,11,F"extensive" damage.
OL,13,FThe US has reacted angrily to the
OL,14,Fstrikes - with President Donald Trump
OL,15,Fthreatening to "massively blow up the
OL,16,Fentirety" of Iran's South Pars natural
OL,17,Fgas field if the country attacks Qatar
OL,18,Fagain.
OL,26,@wD@POUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe wave of Iranian attacks came after
OL,8,FIsrael hit South Pars, the world's
OL,9,Flargest gas field located offshore in
OL,10,Fthe Persian Gulf and owned jointly by
OL,11,FIran and Qatar.
OL,13,FEnergy markets have faced widespread
OL,14,Fdisruption since the US and Israel's
OL,15,Fwar with Iran began on February 28,
OL,16,Fwhich has seen strikes carried out on
OL,17,Fenergy facilities and other targets in
OL,18,Foil-rich Gulf states allied with the
OL,19,FUS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
