PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FStarmer chaired an emergency Cobra
OL,13,Fmeeting on Thursday morning amid
OL,14,Fconcerns about the impact of the
OL,15,Fconflict on domestic energy prices.
OL,17,FUK natural gas prices spiked by more
OL,18,Fthan 20% on Thursday morning, while
OL,19,Fthe latest figures suggest that the
OL,20,Fprice of Brent crude oil has risen by
OL,21,Faround 8%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe government announced a #53 million
OL,8,Fpackage of extra cost-of-living
OL,9,Fsupport on Monday - but the latest
OL,10,Fattacks in the Middle East have raised
OL,11,Fconcerns about what more can be done
OL,12,Fto keep prices down.
OL,14,FCobra meetings - or Cabinet Office
OL,15,FBriefing Room A meetings - form a key
OL,16,Fpart in planning how the government
OL,17,Fcan quickly respond to issues of
OL,18,Fconcern - like the consequences of the
OL,19,Fwar in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThey bring together ministers, civil
OL,8,Fservants and intelligence figures to
OL,9,Fcoordinate the government's response
OL,10,Fto national or international crises -
OL,11,Fsuch as the war in Iran.
OL,13,FMinisters have been meeting regularly
OL,14,Fto discuss the impacts of the war in
OL,15,Fthe Middle East, with Thursday's
OL,16,Fmeeting thought to be in response to
OL,17,Fthe latest tit for tat attacks across
OL,18,Fthe region - and the impact on
OL,19,Fdomestic energy prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FPoliticians across Westminster have
OL,8,Fcalled for the government to take
OL,9,Ffurther action on energy prices.
OL,11,FThey have called on Starmer to give
OL,12,Fmore support to households exposed to
OL,13,Frising heating oil costs - and to
OL,14,Furgently introduce a price cap on this
OL,15,Fkind of energy supply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,8,Furged Starmer to host an emergency
OL,9,FCobra meeting and take action to
OL,10,Fprotect households from what he called
OL,11,Fan "impending #500 bombshell set to
OL,12,Fdevastate family finances".
OL,14,FThe Conservatives have focused their
OL,15,Fefforts on pushing the government to
OL,16,Freverse a planned increase in fuel
OL,17,Fduty - the tax people pay on petrol
OL,18,Fand diesel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
