PN,31313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773997500
OL,3,CStarmer 'condemns in the strongest
OL,4,Cterms' Iran attacks, as UK steps up
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe tax is due to rise by 5p in
OL,8,FSeptember - an increase which the
OL,9,FShadow Transport Secretary Richard
OL,10,FHolden branded "egregious".
OL,12,F"This House has come together to hear
OL,13,Fof yet another egregious tax on
OL,14,Ftransport pushed out by this Labour
OL,15,Fgovernment at a time when people
OL,16,Facross the country are worried about
OL,17,Fthe cost of getting around," he told
OL,18,Fthe Commons on Wednesday.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
